snippet.title: Morbid: The Seven Acolytes - Launch Trailer
snippet.description: Out Now on PlayStation 4, Xbox One, Steam and Nintendo Switch! Morbid: The Seven Acolytes is a Horrorpunk Action RPG filled with Lovecraftian horrors and Cronenbergian gore, making it the most gruesome take on the isometric Souls-like genre yet!
